        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post 303 E 15th Ave, Anchorage, AK 99501 Searching for something more intimate? Our 1 & 2 bedroom apartments in Anchorage, Alaska are ideal if you’re looking for comfort and convenience at the same time. At Kings Court Apartments, you get to live in a welcoming neighborhood, surrounded by nature, but without giving up on the opportunities a big city offers. Plus, we are pet-friendly, so bring your furry friends with you! Apartment Features: Electronic Thermostat Disposal Plush Carpeting Dishwasher Hard-style plank flooring Stove and Oven Range Window Blinds Refrigerator Fireplace in select units Community Features: Pet Friendly Community Close to nightlife, including Williwaw Social Flexible Rent 15-minute drive to Joint Base Elmendorf-Richardson 3 minutes from 5th Avenue Mall A Non-Smoking Community Convenient access to the Anchorage Train Station Laundry Facilities Elevator Located near the Anchorage Museum Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://redtailliving.com/7exl2lbh/kings-court Pricing and availability are subject to change.",
